          <div class="callout-label">⚡ TL;DR — Pick by job</div>
          <p><strong>Pure volume, raw drafts:</strong> Byword — best quality at scale. <strong>Done-for-you publishing:</strong> theStacc — only platform here that drafts, optimizes, and auto-publishes. <strong>CSV-driven on a budget:</strong> Autoblogging.ai or SEOWriting.ai at $19–$49/mo. <strong>Affiliate content:</strong> Koala.sh.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want articles on your site, not in your inbox?</h4>
            <p>theStacc drafts, on-pages, and auto-publishes to WordPress, Webflow, or Ghost. <strong>$99/mo for Content SEO.</strong> See it live in 15 minutes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Book a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · No pitch deck</span>
          </div>
