        <ul>
          <li><strong>Brief</strong> — 50 commercial-intent keywords, 1,500-word target, brand voice provided.</li>
          <li><strong>Industries</strong> — e-commerce (product roundups), B2B SaaS (how-to), local services (landing pages).</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — quality score (rubric), per-article cost, time-to-publish, and 90-day indexing rate.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $2,140 across all ten generators.</li>
        </ul>

