          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Will Google penalize bulk-generated content?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google's spam policy targets content created at scale with the primary purpose of manipulating ranks. Helpful, accurate articles do not get penalized for being AI-assisted. The risk is unedited, low-value spam — not bulk publishing on its own.</p></div></div>
